1:43:07 bro is not even in the game but still got stuck by bad luck 😂
 
 
 
But let's be honest, like don't joke around when someone is having asthma... My lil bro got asthma one time and it is getting worse, (ok now my parent already got him in the hospital, But in my opinion we send him like a little too late) suddenly, at some point.. he passed out, the doctor tried everything, flick him on the knee, pinch him on the thigh and arm.. he didn't respond... so they had to rushed my lil to another (advanced) hospital... The fact that he managed to survive while getting him there is mind-blowing. Like the (advanced) hospital is about 1 hour, 30 minutes away. Im glad that he's still alive now🥰
 
btw I'm crying non-stop while this is happening.

Let this be a slap of a lesson to everyone out there including me okay (:

Sorry for my bad english 🙏🏻
